{"tid":1599413,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[幾時再去美領] 美參議院把人權法排進大會議程","createTime":"2019-09-28T03:20:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-28T08:11:22.000Z","uid":231583,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5e972cf0a13644a02f17eff0b6f599a749428508","tid":1599413,"uid":231583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T03:20:25.000Z","msg":"美國美國參議院已把《香港人權與民主法案》編排進大會議程，可隨時付諸辯論或表決。 <br />\n<br />\n外交關係委員會早前通過受理法案後已向大會匯報，於美國當地周四排進大會的一般議程。按照議事規則及慣例，法案可按照兩黨領袖及議員的意向，付諸辯論或表決，如投票表決的話，只需簡單多數、即全體議員過半數的五十一人或以上同意便可通過法案，餘下程序包括由眾議院審議及總統簽署。 <br />\n<br />\n早前有議員提出「加辣」修訂，包括要求監察特區政府有否自我削弱自治權，及要求國務卿提交證書，證明香港有足夠自治權。<br />\n<br />\nSource: 有線新聞TG<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b637729463f2fb2e8e73366deb8d5c00c90b9045","tid":1599413,"uid":259321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T03:21:26.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PqHqyQK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPqHqyQK.jpg&h=0796b3a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">前線請留低你嘅DNA!!!</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sCHujkN.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsCHujkN.gif&h=37db3acb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2Do9jmF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2Do9jmF.jpg&h=efc8703c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ys8JoOj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fys8JoOj.png&h=2d0ace40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</div>"},{"pid":"e8e71a02801f2b909bbc6844c66955f5408cd7df","tid":1599413,"uid":231583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T03:29:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1542aca3a9597044f2505035e843213750ad080","tid":1599413,"uid":322304,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T03:32:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bd31ab61a865e78b37c771331d8bb0165377fc61","tid":1599413,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T03:39:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cb194d77fc7e3587e0932393a4b0f3df7476020","tid":1599413,"uid":231583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T03:51:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee0b6dabb1e2a552e959869250b7ca5a54c399c8","tid":1599413,"uid":231583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T03:52:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88c5b391ec283855584cbe9bb0995585cf36a83f","tid":1599413,"uid":231583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T03:56:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a310850332da3e78571c818e8050d25074202c73","tid":1599413,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T04:06:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33c03d17d1e8976a3d0329533e135bb09719069e","tid":1599413,"uid":265839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T04:08:28.000Z","msg":"記得多謝人地呀"},{"pid":"e4d3aede8b348172c5b69cffa2101e1b327c8453","tid":1599413,"uid":231583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T04:29:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31f4011ec18e63fe76b7fa9a3742dd0e51040de8","tid":1599413,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T04:42:52.000Z","msg":"支持！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c87dcfdc8f6fdb69d06ce07323c714ea1b1e4d9f","tid":1599413,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T07:38:23.000Z","msg":"全民核彈！全部軍師立即響應美國，草擬制裁港共企業名單！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1599761\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1599761</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"88eb737f9927020ece4e4e27454a8e6a4156fb8d","tid":1599413,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T08:11:22.000Z","msg":"全民核彈！全部軍師立即響應美國，草擬制裁港共企業名單！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1599761\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1599761</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">美國已經批准審核香港人權及民主法案2019，<span style=\"color: red;\">國會議員可以制定制裁名單。</span><br />\n請各位軍師善用呢個機會，<span style=\"color: gold;\">依家大家應搜集一切過往新聞片段、照片、新聞報導、政府新聞公告等一切資料，羅列所有協助侵犯香港人權嘅個人、企業嘅罪證</span>，<span style=\"color: red;\">整理好一份名單，寄俾美國嘅國會議員</span>。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">只要佢哋落入《全球馬格尼茨基人權問責法案》嘅制裁名單，咁個人或公司經濟即刻受到重創。咁呢班商人到時就會調轉槍頭，向政府施壓要求政府讓步及妥協。</span><br />\n我在此拋磚引玉，請大家接力發掘：<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">香港警察</span></strong>：非法鎮壓、濫捕和平示威者，無顯示警員編號及無出示委任證，應全體受到制裁。所以請大家依家要整理好現役警員清單。<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">律政司</span></strong>：無理監控<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">政府新聞處</span></strong>：惡意抹黑示威者，為港共政權掩飾罪證。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>黨鐵</strong></span>：多次協助警察鎮壓示威者，721車務控制中心落order迫停列車，任由黑幫恐怖襲擊。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>新雄雞</strong></span>：縱容警察在其屬下商場毆打、濫捕示威者<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">狗巴、八達通</span></strong>：將示威者八達通資料交與警察抓捕<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">中國國務院港澳辦、中國外交部、中聯辦、人民日報、中央電視台、環球時報、太公文匯報、賣過百份報、黨媒01、巫線、腥賭日報</span></strong>：惡意抹黑示威者，散播仇恨言論，為港共政權掩飾罪證。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>富臨</strong></span>：主動為參與鎮壓和平示威者嘅黑幫提供膳食。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>國家民航局、國泰、拮野家</strong></span>：打壓參與示威嘅員工、或以政治原因炒員工<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>中國政法委</strong></span>：打壓及恐嚇李嘉誠同情年輕人的言論<br />\n等等。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">我地要做嘅係，向美國參眾議員建議制裁名單及佢地罪證。一旦制裁名單上嘅人士、企業受到美國制裁，以後就無人及公司可以同佢做生意。否則同受制裁。</span></strong></span>例子如下：</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>中國企業違反伊朗制裁令　美國務卿：將進行懲罰</strong><br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">美國國務卿龐皮歐（Mike Pompeo）周三（9/25）表示，部分中國公司及個人因違反伊朗制裁禁令，而正接受美國的相關制裁。\n&nbsp;\n美國之音報導，美國財政部周三在其官網上公佈了這次最新制裁的對象，包括5名中國公民和6家中國實體。龐皮歐在紐約聯大會議期間參加一次會議時說：「正如我們對中國和所有國家所說的那樣：要知道我們將對每一次違反禁令進行制裁。」\n&nbsp;\n龐皮歐還說，華府正努力讓各國了解跟伊朗革命衛隊做生意的風險，美國將懲罰那些違反制裁並且繼續跟伊朗接觸的實體和個人。\n&nbsp;\n據悉，這6家被制裁的中國實體是中遠海運（大連）有限公司、大連中遠海運油運船員船舶管理有限公司、中和石油有限公司、昆侖航運有限公司，昆侖控股有限公司和飛馬88有限公司。\nhttps://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190926/1639203</code></pre>"}]}